{"tid":1213370,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"入黎認真討論一下防具","createTime":"2019-06-13T01:26:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-30T05:17:10.000Z","uid":256196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"361c742fef44a5f89c0ae3cdfe99bd75f5d652d9","tid":1213370,"uid":256196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:26:51.000Z","msg":"發夢見到某日子衝擊立法會輸左 武器反攻先唔好講住<br />\n防具唔夠的確係主因 短期內要搵到較容易購買既防具<br />\n如濾毒面罩 頭盔 手甲可以搵報紙雜誌頂住當<br />\n長遠需要全身單車裝等等有耐久度既裝甲<br />\n<br />\n我唔係呢方面專家 希望各位巴打多多補充<br />\n<br />\n利申 尋日發夢輸得好慘 食左一兩棍 好心痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d579121aa7e2d8f6201543d2b1ce43327eaa6f17","tid":1213370,"uid":256196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:28:44.000Z","msg":"保護義士 人人有責<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a9776a67290a0f0ca1fcede6bb58d72bc578287","tid":1213370,"uid":256196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-13T01:30:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e4ed4af40be2789ce506d5ae2eff18b51a4e58","tid":1213370,"uid":90182,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-30T05:17:10.000Z","msg":"善心突破零回覆"}]}